description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 12, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 12, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, 3 for South, and Box for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60121-11340-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [12 Votes, Common]
